headline: Corpay Cross-Border Named an Official Partner of Real Madrid C.F.
summary: TORONTO, June 02, 2025--Corpay, Inc.*, (NYSE: CPAY) a global leader in corporate payments, is pleased to announce that Corpay’s Cross-Border business has entered into an agreement with Real Madrid C.F. to become an Official Partner.
